### Bad Token - 401 Authentication Error
### Invalid or expired PAT token
### Expected: 401 with authentication_error

GET {{host}}/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_or_expired

### Expected Response (OpenAI format):
### {
###   "error": {
###     "type": "authentication_error",
###     "message": "Invalid or expired token",
###     "param": null,
###     "code": "invalid_token"
###   }
### }


### Malformed Body - 400 Invalid Request
### Invalid JSON or missing required fields
### Expected: 400 with invalid_request_error

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o"
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user"
      "content": "Hello"
    }
  ]
}

### Alternative: Missing model field

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello"
    }
  ]
}


### Rate Limit Scenario - 429 Too Many Requests
### Exceeded RPM/TPM limits
### Expected: 429 with rate_limit_exceeded

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Test rate limit"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 10
}

### Note: This may require running many requests to trigger actual rate limiting


### Quota Exceeded - 429 Quota Exceeded
### Monthly budget exhausted
### Expected: 429 with quota_exceeded

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Generate a very long response that will use significant quota"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 4000
}


### Service Unavailable - 503 No Fallback
### Circuit breaker open and no fallback available
### Expected: 503 with service_unavailable

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "claude-haiku-4-5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 10
}
